Package: ffmpegp
Version: 1.30
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: python, python-pip, jq, ffmpeg
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/ankushbhagats/ffmpegp
Description: Python Utility for FFmpeg and FFprobe Operations
 ffmpegp simplifies working with media files using FFprobe and FFmpeg.
 Provides easy extraction of media details, format conversions, and
 advanced JSON path querying with a convenient Python interface.
